messages.message: Hi there! Let's learn how to play together... Use ← and → to move
Now you should see it. Pretty anoying walking in the dark, right? That's why I put torches all over the place. Jump over it, use ↑ or space to do it.
The goal of each level is to reach the red spiraly thing to your right. Go on, that will be all for now...
The dark green square invert the red blocks. The ones that blocked you now let you pass through, and vice-versa.
Passing through a red portal teleports you to the nearest red portal. Keep in mind that your inertia is inchanged!
The blue portals are quite similar, but invert your inertia.
That's the end of the level. Be prepared to die in the next level, just saying...
This one seems a little bit high... Try to jump on the brown circle on your right.
Pretty cool right? Jump Pads allow you to reach higher spots.
Even with a Jump Pad, the next level seems quite far. Maybe with these blue circles...
Gravity Pads invert the gravity. You can reach the next level now!
What you just step into is water. It prevents you from seeing torches, but allows you to freely swim.
Let's make it simple.. Acid kills you.
A bit more vicious, lasers can kill you too. Their beam will be stop by any obstacle though...
